engine of some sort is applying a constant moment which is what causes it to spin. You estimate that it has a mass of [`m = [$m]\ \textrm{kg}`] and a radius of gyration 
of [`k_G = [$kG]\ \textrm{m}`]. In the video you observe the UFO to rotate [`[$theta]`] revolutions. Given the information and speculations present, what is the applied moment, and what is the work done by the moment?

